      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LET'S GO LEGEND (3) looks close to another win after finishing third last time (19.02) at Temora. Form here at the trip sound including five wins. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Deserves a win and gets his chance. CAWBOURNE LADY (7) was fast away from wide out with an impressive early sectional and went on to clock 30.17 in a 0.8 lengths win at this track over 525m. Ran the fastest time on the program in her latest win. One of the key runners again. DING'S SANDY (4) was strong over this course and distance last time despite filling the minors, finishing 0.8 lengths behind CAWBOURNE LADY in 30.21 and recording a new PB here. Looks a leading chance again. WEST END LASS (8) has strong claims after a top-three finish last time out.",
